const colorMap = new Map([]);

function getColor(title) {
    let color;
    if (!colorMap.has(title)) {
        const randomNumber = Math.floor((Math.random() * predeterminedColors.length));
        colorMap.set(title, predeterminedColors[randomNumber]);
        color = predeterminedColors[randomNumber];
        predeterminedColors.splice(randomNumber, randomNumber + 1);
    } else {
        color = colorMap.get(title);
    }
    return color;
}

export default { getColor };
